precis:
Authority to enter into a CONTRIBUTION AGREEMENT with the NORTHWEST
TERRITORIES whereby the federal government will make a financial
contribution towards the implementation of the motor carrier safety
standards outlined in the NATIONAL SAFETY CODE.
